data.description: Come home to your beautiful move-in ready condo, and relax to a gorgeous lake view from the living room and large, master bedroom. Waking up to the morning dawn and reflection off the water from bed is enough to get anyone excited about their day. Screened in patio. 1 month old AC Unit! New flooring throughout the unit. Remodeled kitchen with whirlpool appliances w/ new granite. Remodeled master bath w/ dimming shower lights, rain shower, and elevated ceiling. New custom closets in both bedrooms. Complex has 3 pools, gym, tennis, fishing, boating, restaurant and clubhouse. Hot tubs next to each of the pools and 24hour manned security. HOA includes water, trash removal, sewer, maintenance, security, cable includes HBO & Showtime and more. Last month's deposit can be paid in installments!
